steps.name: user navigates to Login page
Login with Production Manager
Click on the SignIn button
user navigates to Revised Fabric Sheet
click on Styles expansion
click on clear filter icon
Verify whether the user is able to Select an IPO from the Menu list
Click on the Style ShowHide button for closing the menu list
Verify the count of the Fabric records under the Fabric Details grid
click on Add data button
Verify whether the Import popup window is opened when clicked on the Import Fabric Details button
Click on Close button in the Import popup window
Select the WithInIPO option in the Import window
Verify whether Mandatory validation msg is displayed or not on Onclick the Import button without selecting any values
Verify whether the user is able to add the selected fabric on Importing
Select the OtherIPO option in the Import window
Verify whether Mandatory validation msg is displayed or not on Onclick the Import button without selecting any value
Verify whether the user is able to select an IPO in the dropdown or not
Verify whether the Select Fabric field is displayed or not
Verify whether the user is able to add the selected fabric on Importing or not
Select the PDFDS option in the Import window
Verify whether mandatory validation msg is displayed or not on Onclick the Import button without selecting any values
Verify whether the user is able to add the Selected Fabric on Importing
Verify whether the imported fabric is able to Submit to the Fabric Team or not
